data.description: 'ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS'I'm so excited to tell you all about this incredible 5 bedroom, 4 bathroom, 4000 square-foot home in Branson, Missouri. It's located near the popular Kanakuk Kamps and all the amazing attractions in the area.  This home is an absolute gem, offering not only ample space but also a touch of luxury. With its spacious layout, you'll have plenty of room to relax and entertain family and friends. The 5 bedrooms provide a cozy haven for everyone, and the 4 bathrooms ensure convenience and comfort for all. More amazing features of this home include a separate entrance for living quarters with a second kitchen and laundry!  This unique setup offers so much flexibility and convenience. Whether you want to use it as a guest suite, a separate living space for family members, or even as a potential rental opportunity, the possibilities are endless. This home also boasts two decks, one on the upper level and one on the lower level, where you can relax, entertain, and enjoy the beautiful surroundings. Plus, there's additional parking in the back of the house, ensuring that you and your guests have plenty of space.  Whether you're looking for a permanent residence or a vacation home, this property has it all. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own a spacious home on a 1.4-acre lot in Branson, Missouri.
